Socialite and businessman, Pretty Mike stormed a 60th birthday party with three ladies wearing animal masks.
Pretty Mike, known for his dramatic entrances at events shared photos, saying, “We are all animals one way or the other, something drives me crazy about this way of life #BeastMood… It’s too deep for me to explain.
My entrance to ObaBest “Mom” 60th birthday. You should have all seen the look on mummy’s face.”
 
